frames.caption: A majestic falcon is captured mid-flight against a backdrop of rugged cliffs. The sunlight illuminates its wings, creating a striking contrast with the shadowed canyon below.
frames.description: The scene depicts a falcon soaring gracefully near a cliff edge during sunset. The warm glow of the setting sun highlights the bird's feathers, adding a dramatic effect to the natural landscape.

frames.caption: A majestic bird of prey soars gracefully over a canyon, its wings illuminated by the warm glow of the setting sun. The landscape below is bathed in golden light, highlighting the rugged cliffs and expansive horizon.
frames.description: The scene captures a bird in flight over a canyon during sunset. The sun casts a warm, golden light over the landscape, creating a serene and majestic atmosphere.
